{"tid":2194109,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"8.31灣仔暴動案 社工陳虹秀等八人受審","createTime":"2020-09-08T10:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T11:07:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5cd5c4908da629888fa3b1ddc77bfa849ac1e94f","tid":2194109,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:04:51.000Z","msg":"去年8.31港島嚴重警民衝突中，包括「陣地社工」成員陳虹秀等8人被控暴動等罪，案件今早在區域法院開審。主控官今日將控罪範圍由「灣仔軒尼詩道22號及盧押道一帶」修改「灣仔軒尼詩道及盧押道一帶」。法官沈小民指「一帶」有很多意思，要求控方以地圖顯示暴動範圍，「如果唔係你寫『香港』都得啦」。另外，控方要求法庭引用《刑事罪行條例》，即使法官裁定各被告暴動罪名不成立，亦可裁定各人較輕的非法集結罪名成立，有辯方律師對此表示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/XYY4TQXVFJF2HLA6HRH4CJ6Q6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FXYY4TQXVFJF2HLA6HRH4CJ6Q6E%2F&d=pZTDRaRh7CFw%2FURiZY0DNaS5T01Y9%2BWuDWMC0%2BQyx7Y%3D&h=13098688\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200908%2FXYY4TQXVFJF2HLA6HRH4CJ6Q6E%2F&h=4e5aa5af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200908/XYY4TQXVFJF2HLA6HRH4CJ6Q6E/</a>"},{"pid":"0ec530fc433097a9576c41836a8848f288384982","tid":2194109,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:12:08.000Z","msg":"小學雞，預告唔入又要煩住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"731bba1e44a7cdbdedd556da09e7dd29452760e1","tid":2194109,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"控方要求法庭引用《刑事罪行條例》，即使法官裁定各被告暴動罪名不成立，亦可裁定各人較輕的非法集結罪名成立，有辯方律師對此表示不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁不如以後咩都試下 告到告得入為止啊笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd897c151b0c85f7d1bb9486225f6282dc0083e6","tid":2194109,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"731bba1e44a7cdbdedd556da09e7dd29452760e1","tid":2194